summary: Adds some new non replacer tracks into the game.
descriptionHtml:
* I'm gathering talents to make the massive unofficial DLC Dominion, urgently need CK workers, voice actors/actresses/editors, papyrus scripters!
Visit this page to know more: http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/topic/1279053-the-elder-scrolls-v-dominion-recruiting-talents/*


Dude, lass, I'm exhausted and wanna sleep. Not gonna make a nice description/creidts this time.

This mod adds some new non replacer tracks made by different companies into the game.

If you tried it out and think it's good, keep it; if not, uninstall.

Perhaps I'll make a list of the tracks added.

Credits:
No_Aardvarks_Allowed for Personalized Music - Add your own music to Skyrim
Bethesda for Skyrim
Bethesda for Dragonborn
Blizzard Entertainment for the World of Warcraft, Reaper of Souls tracks
ZeniMax Online Studios for the Elder Scrolls Online tracks
Two Steps From Hell
Audiomachine


Legality problem? Comment, no PM. I hate secrets.
If turns out it's illegal to release a mod containing the above companies' creations, I'll remove the files from Nexus instantly.
